    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p>Examples modifying <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a> – <ul>
                    <li>past tense – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>An robh Calum ag iasgach air an loch an dé? Bha.</gd>
                                <tr>Was Malcolm fishing on the lake yesterday? Yes, he was.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>An robh an clachair ag obair air a’ bhalla fad an latha an
                                        dé? Cha robh.</gd>
                                <tr>Was the mason working on the wall all day yesterday? No, he
                                    wasn’t.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 20 [adapted]</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Bha mi anns a’ mhonadh an dé. Chunnaic mi caoraich agus crodh
                                    anns a’ mhonadh.</gd>
                                <tr>I was on the moor yesterday. I saw sheep and cattle on the
                                    moor.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 21</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
